collection.name: CyberKongz
collection.description:
Welcome to an alternate reality, where evolution took a different route and weird apes roam the earth.
Some appear normal. Some look weird. And some are just damn cool! 
Every CyberKong is unique and owns randomized items with different rarities. A few are super rare and even animated!
**Maybe some of them look familiar!**  
   
[More CyberKongz Collections!](https://opensea.io/collection/cyberkongz-nfts)  
[Website](https://cyberkongz.com) | [Twitter](https://twitter.com/cyberkongz) | [Discord](https://discord.gg/cyberkongz)
